item.title: 【Requests】[REQ CAP] - Jung Kook - Album Release Party
item.description:
Jungkook will be on iHeartRadio! ❤️‍

An Album Release Party will be held for 'GOLDEN' on Friday, November 3rd. During it, Jungkook will perform some of his new songs, as well as talk about 'GOLDEN' and more during a special Q&A session hosted by iHeartRadio's JoJo Wright.

Fans will be able to tune in to Hit Nation and iHeartRadio's K-Pop Radio station. Could someone record this show? Please!
